                <note rend="inline" type="source">818.00/803: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul at San José</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Chase</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">San José</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-08-01T17:00:00-05:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 1, 1919, 5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[<hi rend="italic">Received August 4, 11.25 a.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Federico Tinoco in Congress this afternoon asked its permission to leave the
                    country on account of illness but he said nothing about resignation. Every
                    indication a complete change in the government very soon. Joaquin said farewell
                    to the police this morning.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Chase</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
